<p>Given the city's air quality concerns and dense urban environment, investing in high-quality air filtration and ventilation is essential. Energy Recovery Ventilators (ERVs) help maintain indoor air quality while minimizing energy loss during the heating season. Smart thermostats and zoned systems maximize efficiency in buildings where space heating can account for 40-50% of annual energy consumption.</p>

<h2>New York City Energy Incentives</h2>
