<p>NYSERDA's EmPower+ program provides additional HVAC rebates and financing options for income-qualified residents, while the city's Property Assessed Clean Energy (PACE) financing allows property owners to finance solar and HVAC improvements through property tax assessments. These combined incentives can reduce total project costs by 40-60% for qualifying installations.</p>

